trans-unit.source: Exposes a means of generating client proxy classes for XML Web services.
trans-unit.target: Expõe um meio de gerar as classes de proxy do cliente para serviços Web de XML.

trans-unit.source: The interface to an XML Web service is typically described by a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) file.
trans-unit.target: A interface para um serviço XML Web service normalmente é descrita por um ficheiro Web Services Description Language (WSDL).

trans-unit.source: For example, to obtain a WSDL description of a Web service using ASP.NET exposed at `http://localhost/service.asmx`, simply navigate to `http://localhost/service.asmx?WSDL`.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo obter uma descrição de WSDL de um serviço Web utilização do ASP.NET expostos na `http://localhost/service.asmx`, basta navegar para `http://localhost/service.asmx?WSDL`.

trans-unit.source: The ServiceDescriptionImporter class allows you to easily import the information contained in a WSDL description into a <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit?displayProperty=fullName> object.
trans-unit.target: A classe de ServiceDescriptionImporter permite-lhe importar facilmente as informações contidas numa descrição WSDL para um <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit?displayProperty=fullName>objeto.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: By adjusting the value of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A> parameter, you can instruct a ServiceDescriptionImporter instance either to generate a client proxy class that provides the functionality of the Web service by transparently calling it or to generate an abstract class that encapsulates the functionality of the Web service without implementing it.
trans-unit.target: Ao ajustar o valor do <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A>parâmetro, pode instruir uma instância de ServiceDescriptionImporter para gerar uma classe de proxy do cliente que fornece a funcionalidade do serviço Web chamando transparente-lo ou para gerar uma classe abstracta que encapsula a funcionalidade do serviço Web sem implementar a mesma.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: The code in the resulting <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit> object can then either be called directly or exported in the language of your choice.
trans-unit.target: O código resultante <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit>objeto pode, em seguida, ser chamado directamente ou exportado num idioma à sua escolha.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> to the collection of <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> values to be imported.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona especificado <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> à coleção de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>valores a serem importados.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: Use this method to add <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> instances to the collection that is to be imported when the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: Utilize este método para adicionar <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>instâncias para a coleção que está a ser importado quando o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A>método é chamado.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: The two string parameters, `appSettingUrlKey` and `appSettingBaseUrl`, specify how to construct the `Url` property of the XML Web service proxy that is to be generated from the imported <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> value.
trans-unit.target: Os dois parâmetros, de cadeia `appSettingUrlKey` e `appSettingBaseUrl`, especifique como construir o `Url` propriedade o proxy do serviço XML Web que está a ser gerados a partir de importada <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>valor.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>

trans-unit.source: The `appSettingUrlKey` parameter specifies that the `Url` property should be read out of the web.config file's `<appsettings>` section by using the parameter value as the configuration key.
trans-unit.target: O `appSettingUrlKey` parâmetro especifica que o `Url` propriedade deve ser lida fora do ficheiro Web. config `<appsettings>` secção utilizando o valor do parâmetro como a chave de configuração.

trans-unit.source: If the `appSettingUrlKey` parameter is `null` or an empty string, the initial value is determined by the `location` attribute in the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document.
trans-unit.target: Se o `appSettingUrlKey` parâmetro é `null` ou uma cadeia vazia, o valor inicial é determinado pelo `location` atributo no documento Web Services Description Language (WSDL).

trans-unit.source: If the value of <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A> is `Server`, an error is raised if you attempt to set the value of the `appSettingUrlKey` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Se o valor de <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A>é `Server`, é gerado um erro se tentar definir o valor do `appSettingUrlKey` parâmetro.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: The `appSettingBaseUrl` parameter specifies that the initial value for the `Url` property should be constructed from a combination of this parameter value and the URL specified by the `location` attribute in the WSDL document.
trans-unit.target: O `appSettingBaseUrl` parâmetro especifica que o valor inicial para o `Url` propriedade deve ser construída a partir de uma combinação deste valor de parâmetro e o URL especificado pelo `location` atributo no documento WSDL.

trans-unit.source: The `appSettingUrlKey` parameter must also be specified.
trans-unit.target: O `appSettingUrlKey` parâmetro deve ser também especificado.

trans-unit.source: The `Url` property is constructed by combining a relative URL (constructed from the `appSettingBaseUrl` parameter and the WSDL-specified URL) with the URL loaded from the web.config file.
trans-unit.target: O `Url` propriedade é construída através da combinação de um URL relativo (construídas a partir de `appSettingBaseUrl` parâmetro e o URL especificado de WSDL) com o URL carregado a partir do ficheiro Web. config.

trans-unit.source: If this parameter is `null` or an empty string, the URL is constructed entirely from the value in the web.config file.
trans-unit.target: Se este parâmetro for `null` ou uma cadeia vazia, o URL é construída completamente a partir do valor no ficheiro Web. config.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> instance to add to the collection
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> instância a adicionar à coleção

trans-unit.source: Sets the initial value of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Url" name="Url" href=""></xref> property of the proxy class to be generated from the instance represented by the `serviceDescription` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Define o valor inicial do <xref uid="langword_csharp_Url" name="Url" href=""> </xref> propriedade da classe de proxy gerado na instância representado pelo `serviceDescription` parâmetro.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that it should be generated from the web.config file's <xref uid="langword_csharp_<appsetting>" name="<appsetting>" href=""></xref> section.
trans-unit.target: Especifica que deve ser gerado no ficheiro Web. config <xref uid="langword_csharp_<appsetting>" name="<appsetting>" href=""> </xref> secção.

trans-unit.source: Sets the initial value of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Url" name="Url" href=""></xref> property of the proxy class to be generated from the instance represented by the `serviceDescription` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Define o valor inicial do <xref uid="langword_csharp_Url" name="Url" href=""> </xref> propriedade da classe de proxy gerado na instância representado pelo `serviceDescription` parâmetro.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that it should be constructed from a combination of the value of this parameter and the URL specified by the <xref uid="langword_csharp_location" name="location" href=""></xref> attribute in the WSDL document.
trans-unit.target: Especifica que deve ser criada a partir de uma combinação do valor deste parâmetro e o URL especificado pelo <xref uid="langword_csharp_location" name="location" href=""> </xref> atributo no documento WSDL.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets various options for code generation.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define a várias opções para a geração de código.

trans-unit.source: The CodeGenerationOptions property allows you to specify various options used when the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A> method is called to generate code.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade CodeGenerationOptions permite-lhe especificar várias opções utilizadas quando o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A>método denomina-se para gerar código.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Import%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can specify whether simple types described in the WSDL are generated as value types or <xref:System.Data.SqlTypes> namespace types, and whether they are generated as properties or fields.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, pode especificar se os tipos simples descritos no WSDL são gerados como tipos de valor ou <xref:System.Data.SqlTypes>tipos de espaço de nomes, e se são gerados como campos ou propriedades.</xref:System.Data.SqlTypes>

trans-unit.source: A member or combination of members of the <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.CodeGenerationOptions"></xref> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Um membro ou uma combinação de membros de <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.CodeGenerationOptions"> </xref> enumeração.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the code generator used by the service description importer.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o gerador de código utilizado pelo importador de descrição de serviço.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator"></xref> interface used by the service description importer to generate proxy code.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator"> </xref> interface utilizada pelo importador de descrição de serviço para gerar código de proxy.

trans-unit.source: Compiles a collection of Web references to produce a client proxy or a server stub.
trans-unit.target: Compila uma coleção de referências a Web para produzir um proxy do cliente ou um stub de servidor.

trans-unit.source: The services description document collection in each <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference> member of the `webReferences` collection should contain only <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> and <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> objects.
trans-unit.target: A coleção de documentos de descrição de serviços em cada <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference>Membro o `webReferences` coleção deve conter apenas <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription>e <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>objetos.</xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.WebReference>

trans-unit.source: This method is unable to interpret <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument> objects.
trans-unit.target: Este método não é possível interpretar <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument>objetos.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocument>

trans-unit.source: If any of the XML Web service methods in the `webReferences` collection share custom parameter or return types, those types are also shared among the proxy methods generated.
trans-unit.target: Se qualquer um dos XML Web service métodos no `webReferences` coleção partilhar parâmetro personalizado ou tipos de retorno, esses tipos também são partilhados entre os métodos de proxy gerados.

trans-unit.source: This is an important advantage over the situation in which each proxy is compiled separately, because in that case such types do not interoperate.
trans-unit.target: Este é vantagens importantes sobre a situação em que cada proxy é compilado em separado, porque, caso em que esses tipos não interagir.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceCollection"></xref> of Web references to compile.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceCollection"> </xref> de referências a Web para compilar.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"></xref> that specifies the code provider.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"> </xref> que especifica o fornecedor de código.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"></xref> that specifies the unit into which code is compiled.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"> </xref> Especifica que a unidade na qual o código é compilado.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions"></xref> that specifies code generation options.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.WebReferenceOptions"> </xref> que especifica os opções de geração de código.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection"></xref> of compiler warnings.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection"> </xref> avisos de compilador.

trans-unit.source: Imports the specified <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> values, that generates code as specified by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style*> property.
trans-unit.target: Importa especificado <> </> *> valores, o que gera o código como especificado pelo <> </> *> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: After you have specified the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions%2A> values to import and the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A> property of the code to generate, call the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Import> method to initiate code generation.
trans-unit.target: Depois de especificar o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions%2A>valores para importar e a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A>propriedade do código para gerar, chame o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Import>método para iniciar a geração de código.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Import> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.Style%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions%2A>

trans-unit.source: The namespace into which the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> values are imported.
trans-unit.target: O espaço de nomes no qual o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>valores são importados.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"></xref> instance in which the code that represents the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> value is generated.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"> </xref> instância em que o código que representa o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>valor é gerado.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportWarnings"></xref> value that describes any error that occurred; or 0 if no error occurred.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportWarnings"> </xref> valor que descreve quaisquer erros que ocorreram; ou 0 se nenhum erro ocorreu.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the protocol used to access the described XML Web services.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o protocolo utilizado para aceder aos serviços Web de XML descritos.

trans-unit.source: The allowed values of this property are: - "Soap" - "Soap12" - "HttpPost" - "HttpGet" - "HttpSoap" The default value is "Soap", which indicates the SOAP 1.1 standard.
trans-unit.target: Os valores desta propriedade permitidos são: - "Soap" - "Soap12" - "HttpPost" - "HttpGet" - "HttpSoap" o valor predefinido é "Soap", que indica a norma de SOAP 1.1.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the case-insensitive name of the protocol to be imported.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.String>que contém o nome sensível do protocolo a ser importado.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas"></xref> used by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> property.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas"> </xref> utilizado pelo <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas"></xref> object that contains the XML schemas used by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> instances in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas"> </xref> objeto que contém os esquemas XML utilizados pelo <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> instâncias no <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>coleção.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> instances to be imported.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a coleção de <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> instâncias a serem importados.

trans-unit.source: As with any collection that forms a read-only property, members can be added to the collection, removed from the collection, or modified using the methods exposed by the collection.
trans-unit.target: À semelhança de qualquer coleção que uma propriedade só de leitura de formulários, membros podem ser adicionados à coleção, removido da coleção ou modificadas utilizando os métodos expostos pela coleção.

trans-unit.source: You can also use the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.AddServiceDescription%2A> method to add members to this collection.
trans-unit.target: Também pode utilizar o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.AddServiceDescription%2A>método para adicionar membros a esta coleção.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.AddServiceDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection"></xref> instance that contains the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"></xref> instances slated to be imported by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection"> </xref> instância que contém o <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription"> </xref> slated instâncias a serem importados pelo <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter"> </xref> instância.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that determines the style of code (client or server) that is generated when the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*> values are imported.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um valor que determina o estilo do código (cliente ou servidor) que é gerado quando o <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>valores são importados.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter.ServiceDescriptions*>

trans-unit.source: If the Style property is set to <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> generates client proxy classes that provide the functionality of the described Web services by calling them.
trans-unit.target: Se a propriedade de estilo estiver definida como <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>, a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>gera classes de proxy do cliente que fornecem a funcionalidade dos serviços Web descritos chamando-los.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>

trans-unit.source: If the Style property is set to <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> instance generates abstract classes that represent the functionality of the described XML Web services without implementing them.
trans-unit.target: Se a propriedade de estilo estiver definida como <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>, a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>instância gera classes abstratas que representam a funcionalidade dos serviços Web de XML descritos sem implementá-las.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle>

trans-unit.source: You can then implement them by writing classes that inherit from these abstract classes and implement the relevant methods.
trans-unit.target: Em seguida, pode implementá-la ao escrever as classes que herdam estas classes abstratas e implementam os métodos relevantes.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Um do <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle"> </xref> valores.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A predefinição é <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportStyle"> </xref>.
